comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Nogueira (TOR) takes a wide stance and makes foot to foot contact with Smart (BOS) on the screen.
Smart (BOS) does not make contact with Lowry (TOR) that affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Crowder (BOS) enters the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
Crowder (BOS) does not beat Lowry (TOR) to the spot and obtain a legal guarding position, and he makes contact that affects the driving shot attempt.
Thomas (BOS) does not have part of his hand under the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Horford (BOS) makes marginal contact with Nogueira (TOR) that does not affect his FOM.
Nogueira (TOR) sets the screen on Smart (BOS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Lowry's (TOR) field goal attempt did not hit the rim is overturned and the shot clock is correctly reset.
[Observable in enhanced video] Lowry (TOR) moves his pivot foot.
There is no clear and conclusive evidence that Smart (BOS) makes contact with Powell (TOR) that affects his shot attempt.
Carroll (TOR) makes marginal contact with Thomas (BOS) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Smart (BOS) moves his pivot foot.
Horford (BOS) sets the screen on Powell (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Powell (TOR) makes marginal contact with Thomas (BOS) that does not affect his driving shot attempt. Nogueira (TOR) makes incidental contact after the blocked shot.
Carroll (TOR) and Powell (TOR) make incidental contact with Smart (BOS) during rebounding.
Carroll (TOR) commits a take foul on Thomas (BOS).
Patterson (TOR) makes marginal contact with Horford (BOS) that does not affect his FOM.
Nogueira (TOR) commits a take foul on Thomas (BOS).
Powell (TOR) commits a take foul on Horford (BOS).
